All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface HierarchicalTypedPropertyNode<K extends Comparable,V,H extends HierarchicalTypedPropertyNode<K,V,H>>
extends Comparable, HierarchyNode<com.davidsoergel.dsutils.collections.OrderedPair<K,V>,H>

Describes a node in a tree containing a key-value pair (at this node) and a set of children. The types of both the key and the value are generic. The children can be retrieved by key, Map-style. Also stores various flags (e.g., nullable, editable, etc.) to support the @Property framework.
